<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>회원 정보 수정</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
    <style>
        .edit-container { max-width: 500px; margin: 50px auto; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 10px; }
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 15px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
        .form-group label { font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 5px; color: #444; }
        .form-group input { padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 14px; }
        .form-group input[readonly] { background-color: #f3f4f6; color: #9ca3af; cursor: not-allowed; }
        .btn-submit { width: 100%; padding: 12px; background-color: #4b5563; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 10px; }
        .btn-submit:hover { background-color: #374151; }
        .back-link { display: block; text-align: center; margin-top: 15px; color: #666; text-decoration: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="edit-container">
    <h2>⚙️ 회원 정보 수정</h2>
    <p style="color: #888; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 20px;">변경할 항목만 입력하세요. 빈칸은 기존 정보가 유지됩니다.</p>

    <form action="/user/edit" method="POST">
        <div class="form-group">
            <label>아이디 (변경 불가)</label>
            <input type="text" name="username" value="<%= user.username %>" readonly>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label>새 비밀번호 (변경 시에만 입력)</label>
            <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="새로운 비밀번호">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label>이름</label>
            <input type="text" name="name" value="<%= user.name %>" placeholder="이름 입력">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label>생년월일</label>
            <input type="text" name="birth" value="<%= user.birth || '' %>" placeholder="예: 20020101">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label>이메일</label>
            <input type="email" name="email" value="<%= user.email || '' %>" placeholder="example@gmail.com">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label>연락처</label>
            <input type="text" name="phone" value="<%= user.phone || '' %>" placeholder="010-XXXX-XXXX">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label>주소지</label>
            <input type="text" name="address" value="<%= user.address || '' %>" placeholder="주소 입력">
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">수정 완료하기</button>
        <a href="/mypage" class="back-link">취소하고 마이페이지로</a>
    </form>
</div>
</body>
</html>